Going all out for Pride this year? We are. 💫  We’re celebrating LGBTQIA+ communities everywhere with an extra-colorful collection of stories (and fits) featuring LGBTQIA+ talent in front of and behind the camera. For all those still planning your Pride looks: good news, our collection is yours to shop online. 

We believe everyone deserves the space to be their authentic self. The Coach Foundation continues to partner with the Hetrick-Martin Institute, Point Foundation and CenterLink Community of LGBTQ Centers to create supportive environments where LGBTQIA+ young people can thrive. #CoachNY

#CourageToBeReal #CoachNY

🏁 Start your engines…  🏁 We’re proud to sponsor @nascar professional driver @tonibreidinger at her upcoming Craftsman Truck Series race this Saturday, June 7.

Toni is the first Arab-American woman to compete in #NASCAR and the only woman racing full-time in a NASCAR top three series. You might also recognize her from our #SohoSneaker campaign, “Not Just For Walking.” We’re inspired by her accomplishments and by who she is as a person: barrier-breaking and unafraid to courageously champion self-expression.

Toni, we’re rooting for you! (And we think your truck looks pretty cool, too.😉)
